#

Gala Apple and Cheese Snack

5 min
$3.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackQuickHealthy

Description

A refreshing and satisfying snack combining the sweetness of Gala apples with the creaminess of cheese, perfect for a quick bite.

Ingredients

  • gala apple: 1 large
  • cheddar cheese: 2 ounces
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • cinnamon: 1/4 teaspoon
